---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab Is Among the Top 10 Start-Ups Worldwide - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab earned 'Top Picks' recognition in RWRC's Discovery 50 Report, representing the ten companies judges believed could transform commerce."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab Is Among the Top 10 Start-Ups Worldwide</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2020-05-30">May 30, 2020</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>4 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          parcelLab has earned "Top Picks" recognition in RWRC's Discovery 50 Report -- representing the ten companies judges believed could transform commerce. The report selected top retail technology startups globally, focusing on companies providing innovative solutions to transform business processes for retailers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">What is the Discovery 50 Report?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          RWRC selected top retail technology startups globally for the Discovery 50 Report. The selection focused on companies providing innovative solutions to transform business processes. Despite coronavirus disruptions, RWRC proceeded with the report, believing innovation timing was crucial for retail adaptation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Why Retailers Should Partner with Startups</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          E-commerce companies often underestimate startup collaboration potential. Innovation-driven direct-to-consumer brands leverage tech infrastructure for rapid growth. Traditional retailers can match this competitive advantage through startup solutions.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">From the Report</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"Fostering start-up partnerships enables retailers to better compete with the growing number of disruptors and direct-to-consumer brands entering the market."</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">parcelLab Featured as a "Top Pick"</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          GlobalData predicted Covid-19 would positively impact e-commerce long-term, creating new customer bases requiring exceptional experiences. The judges highlighted that proactive, personalized communications beyond checkout -- including shipping and delivery updates -- strengthen customer engagement.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Judges' Assessment</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">"parcelLab turns boring shipping information into real communication, offering customers the tools to monitor shipments."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The Discovery 50 recognition validates parcelLab's approach to transforming the post-purchase experience. By helping merchants improve customer experience through shipping communications and engagement solutions, parcelLab supports online retailers during both crises and normal operations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
